'''尤丹諾·范圖拉·赫南德茲''' (Yordano Ventura Hernández; {{IPA-es|ɟʝorˈðano βenˈtuɾa|lang=es}}; {{bd|1991年|6月3日|2017年|1月22日|catIdx=Ventura}})曾是一位隸屬[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]][[堪薩斯市皇家隊|堪薩斯市皇家隊]]的[[職業棒球|職業棒球]][[先發投手|先發投手]]。

他曾兩次獲選入小聯盟[[未來之星明星賽|未來之星明星賽]]，為備受期待的新秀之一。2013年9月17日，范圖拉大聯盟初登板面對[[克里夫蘭印地安人隊|克里夫蘭印地安人隊]]5.2局失1分無關勝負。以[[速球型投手|速球型投手]]知名，他的[[快速球|快速球]]在球員生涯中最快可達102mph(約164km/h)。皇家隊贏得[[2015年世界大賽|2015年世界大賽]]的冠軍隊成員之一。2017年1月22日，范圖拉因車禍而逝世，得年25歲。

==早年生活==
范圖拉於1991年在[[多明尼加共和國|多明尼加共和國]]的[[聖塔芭芭拉-山美納|聖塔芭芭拉-山美納]]出生。他在14歲時輟學後曾於建造業工作一段時間，直至他參加了[[堪薩斯市皇家隊|堪薩斯市皇家隊]]的一個體育學院。<ref name=dreams>{{cite web|url=http://www.kansascity.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/vahe-gregorian/article343428/Yordano-Ventura-has-the-stuff-dreams-are-made-of.html|title=Yordano Ventura has the stuff dreams are made of|first=Vahe|last=Gregorian|work=Kansas City Star|date=March 30, 2014|accessdate=January 22, 2017|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811152344/http://www.kansascity.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/vahe-gregorian/article343428/Yordano-Ventura-has-the-stuff-dreams-are-made-of.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/18531119/kansas-city-royals-right-hander-yordano-ventura-25-killed-car-accident "Royals right-hander Yordano Ventura, 25, killed in car crash"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/18531119/kansas-city-royals-right-hander-yordano-ventura-25-killed-car-accident |date=20170123080839 }}. espn.com. January 22, 2017. Retrieved January 22, 2017.</ref>

==去世==
2017年1月22日, 范圖拉在一場發生於多明尼加共和國{{link-en|Juan Adrián}}的車禍中逝世。<ref name=si>{{cite web|url=http://www.si.com/mlb/2017/01/22/royals-yordano-ventura-dead-car-crash|title=Royals pitcher Yordano Ventura killed in car crash|first=|last=|work=Sports Illustrated|date=January 22, 2017|accessdate=January 22, 2017|archive-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124013439/http://www.si.com/mlb/2017/01/22/royals-yordano-ventura-dead-car-crash|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.elcaribe.com.do/2017/01/22/confirman-yordano-ventura-tragico-accidente-segundo-pelotero-que-muere-este-domingo|title=Confirman es Yordano Ventura el de trágico accidente; es segundo pelotero que muere este domingo|website=El Caribe|language=es|date=January 22, 2017|access-date=January 22, 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123104926/http://www.elcaribe.com.do/2017/01/22/confirman-yordano-ventura-tragico-accidente-segundo-pelotero-que-muere-este-domingo|archivedate=2017年1月23日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/royals-pitcher-yordano-ventura-killed-162153891.html|title=Royals Pitcher Yordano Ventura Was Killed In A Fatal Car Accident In The Dominican Republic|work=Yahoo Sports|first=Robby|last=Kalland|date=January 22, 2017|accessdate=January 22, 2017|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202075033/https://www.yahoo.com/news/royals-pitcher-yordano-ventura-killed-162153891.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

